Package txml.parser

Contains antlr classes (http://www.antlr.org/).

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    XQueryListener
    This interface defines a complete listener for a parse tree produced by XQueryParser.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    XQueryBaseListener
    This class provides an empty implementation of XQueryListener, which can be extended to create a listener which only needs to handle a subset of the available methods.
